Concepts
	deals with tree structures of information
	components represent part or whole structure
	meant to treat components the same 
	compose objects into tree structures
	you can treat individual object as a composite
	some operation applied on individual and composites
	
Examples:
	java.awt.Component
	JSF widgets
	RESTfull services GETs
	
Design
	Tree structure
	Leaf of composite, same operations
	composite knows about child objects
	component, leaf, composite
	
	